  Locus:
    Page: 85
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Death
---
Death is transition. Our body dies and it breaks correspondence with our
physical environment. But our life is in the spirit, and this life is
eternal. Life never dies. Bodies cease, but life is eternal.
